{
  "stem": "5644.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 143,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was engaged mostly, mostly, mostly, food and ammunition and guns from the Christian side, because I knew quite a lot of Christian boys.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 143,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was not the one only, because I did have more people bringing in the guns.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 143,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I was the one which they asked to bring in guns and even machine guns.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 144,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From before the war.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 145,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to school with them and I did have friends which are--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did retain.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I knew and the organization knew well-- and that was the most important thing-- that if I go out when the ghetto was closed or when the ghetto is open, that I can knock at 50 doors which let me in-- which will let me in-- in a way that some may not refuse to let me in.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then I will go out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they won't harm me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No one will harm me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Harm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To advise the Germans that I've been there or the Polish police.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No one will harm me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I got 50 places where I can knock at the door and go in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 148,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Guns and machine guns are not given for nothing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We paid for it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 150,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where did the money come--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 151,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The machine guns.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 152,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mostly I bought them at the Kercelak--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 153,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--which was a market.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 153,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 154,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it's a very funny market there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 155,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One minute.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 156,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The money.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 157,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 158,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 158,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We did-- we buy them from different places.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 158,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But my place was the one which I did want to buy was Kercelak.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 159,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was a market, a Polish market, which was safer for the Jews to be there than in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 160,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because mostly dealers, dealers in black market, dealers in anything you like to think of.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 160,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was a market from before the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
